      <h1 class="heading">Problem</h1>
      <h2 class="solution-h2">
        I saw that numerous people around me had a keen interest in widening
        their knowledge about marine life. However, most of the resources
        available, were not interactive. There were books and articles that one
        could read but one could rarely find an interactive and visual tool to
        fulfill their need. It was difficult for them to understand the complex
        and technical terminologies used in most of these resources. In addition
        to this, some students were facing difficulties in finding reasonable
        resources to learn and study the subjects they relished. Therefore, I
        felt, it was the need of the hour to develop a product that would
        simultaneously combat both these problems.
      </h2>
