      <h1 class="heading">Solution</h1>
      <h2 class="solution-h2">
        Marinomenta is a Web-based platform-cum-application that provides
        interactive insights to Marine life and aspects tangential to it. It
        makes marine life fun, visual, interactive and interesting to learn. It
        is a knowledge building tool that is easy to navigate and accessible.
        Especially for beginners, it provides a learning base and a forum to
        interact with each other. Secondly, it provides a platform where mentors
        can post content for students to learn from. Also, it enables the
        mentors to expand their knowledge by sharing it with others.
      </h2>
